Accept = pd.read_csv('/Users/connorlawhead/Documents/Stony_Brook/social_monetary_RewP/AcceptDiff.Waves.csv',header=None)

heatmapz2 = Accept.T

for column in heatmapz2:
    newval = column - 201
    heatmapz2 = heatmapz2.rename(columns={column: newval})

heatmapz2.index = heatmapz2.index.map(heatmapz3r)
